<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>٢ في <span class="c1">"ط"</span> <span class="c1">"تقاتلوا"</span>.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>٣ المقنع مع الشرح الكبير والإنصاف <span class="c1">"١٠/٤٩١"</span>.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
